description: Number of conjugacy classes of compact Cartan subgroups in Sp_{2n}(F), where p>n and the p-adic field F contains all r-th roots of unity for all r <= 2n.
references: L. Morris, Some tamely ramified supercuspidal representations of symplectic groups, Proc. London Math. Soc., 63 (1991), 519-551.
author: Jeff Adler (adler(AT)uakron.edu)
